Grupos: U2, PJ Harvey, Brandy, Seal, Massive Attack, Eddi Reader, Mazzy Star, Offspring, Nick Cave, Method Man, Michael Hutchence, The Devlins, Sunny Day Real State, Flaming Lips
Lançamento: Warner
Preço: R$ 20 (o CD, em média)
